name: realityLamp
0:
”Alexa, reality lamp.”
”Alexa, ask reality lamp to read book.”
”Alexa, ask reality lamp to scan receipt.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: reality lamp
des:
Say reality lamp as invocation ,than say read book or other.
rRead book" returns a paragraph of text, "scan receipt" returns text like "title is {}, date is {}, amount is {}.", "complete scan" returns text like "The total amount of receipts is {} dollars. "
